resources.string:
The main Cadpage app no longer supports anything before Android 4.0. This is a variant that will continue to be maintained to support users back to Android 2.3. Updates may be infrequent. And it looks like I will loose the ability to distribute them through Google Play Store on November 1. We will have to wait and see what happens then.
